init(ServletConfig) - Method in class il.ac.hit.taxitogo.controller.TaxiToGoController
Called by the servlet container to indicate to a servlet that the servlet is being placed into service.
The servlet container calls the init method after instantiating the servlet.
The init method must complete successfully before the servlet can receive any requests.
The web container also initializes the property file and it writes a log message inside the log-file.
